cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CL 

This paper is about improving the performance of object detectors using a learning technique, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). The technique involves feeding in localization information to the network, which is related to neural networks (cs.NE) and natural language processing (cs.CL) where attention mechanisms are commonly used.
